tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_rating INT,
  feedback_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE feedback_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE customer_profiles (customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_name TEXT,
  email TEXT,
  phone_number TEXT);

CREATE TABLE retention_strategies (strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_description TEXT,
  target_audience TEXT,
  achievement_goal TEXT);

CREATE TABLE feedback_analysis (analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  analysis_result TEXT,
  improvement_goals TEXT);

CREATE TABLE customer_profiles ( 
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    customer_name TEXT, 
    email_address TEXT, 
    registration_date DATE, 
    last_purchase_date DATE 
);
